name: The King Teux
description:
Discovered : 3150 BCE

Known as "The Dangerous One", King Teux is a potent, highly-alcoholic being that rules the spirit realm. Hailing from the powerful concoction Absinthe, many fear the King for its raging flammability. Yet, the same ferocity is what causes many to still serve it in worship even to this day. All hail the King!
